name: Shimano Sedona Spinning Reel
categoryPath: Sports & Outdoors/Outdoor Sports/Fishing/Fishing Rods & Reels/Fishing Reels

reviews.name: Shimano Sedona Spinning Reel
reviews.reviewText: I am very pleased with this reel. It has a very smooth retrieve and no issues with back lash. This is my second Shimano reel and this one is better than the first one. Shimano keeps improving on their quality of fishing reels. I am looking forward to using it this weekend, doing some trout fishing in western NC! Great price, Walmart had the lowest price with free shipping.
reviews.title: Excellent reel for the price!

reviews.name: Shimano Sedona Spinning Reel
reviews.reviewText: The sedona is a good but for the price, looks and performs like an expensive model.
reviews.title: Very good
